<DOCID> 092459 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
October 27, 1994, Thursday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Part F; Page 3; Column 4; Entertainment Desk 
