fellowship this week by the National Football Foundation and College Hall of 
Fame, said he would use the grant for graduate school after a pro career. 
</P>
<P>
 "I'll get an MBA, something like that," he said. "It's a great honor and I'm 
really thrilled about it." 
</P>
<P>
