Trojans in his senior season. 
</P>
<P>
 Bender joined the Raiders as a free agent last spring. 
</P>
<P>
 "He's a tremendous blocker," Coach Art Shell said. 
</P>
<P>
 Bender will back up fullback Tom Rathman and also play on special teams. 
