<DOCNO> LA102794-0168 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 092571 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
October 27, 1994, Thursday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Long Beach; Part J; Page 2 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
