<HEADLINE>
<P>
NOMINATIONS OPEN FOR FAMILY OF THE YEAR 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Nominations for La Palma Family of the Year are being accepted through Friday 
by the city's Recreation and Community Services Department office in Central 
Park, 7821 Walker St. 
</P>
<P>
 The winning family and all nominated families will be recognized at the City 
Council meeting Nov. 15. 
</P>
<P>
 The competition is being coordinated by the city's Cultural and Beautification 
Committee. Nomination forms are available at Central Park, City Hall, the 
library and from various churches and service organizations throughout the 
city. 
</P>
