 * What Happened Wednesday: Democrat Kathleen Brown held news conferences in 
San Francisco and Los Angeles to announce a proposed overhaul of California's 
environmental regulations to streamline government and encourage economic 
development. That goal can be achieved without sacrificing the effectiveness of 
