<DOCNO> LA102794-0332 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 092735 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
October 27, 1994, Thursday, Ventura West Edition 
</P>
