 Show time is 8 p.m. both nights. Tickets are $7 (general), $5 (students and 
children under age 12 -- though the play is not recommended for those under age 
13 due to "strong language"). Call 963-0408. The theater is located on the 
second level of the Paseo Nuevo shopping center. 
</P>
<P>
