</P>
<P>
 Imagine watching actor William Devane and former Monkee Mickey Dolenz battle 
it out on the polo field? A little surreal, perhaps, but they will be two of 
the celebrities involved, Saturday in a Santa Barbara Civic Light Opera benefit 
dubbed "An Afternoon of Polo and Other Pleasures." 
</P>
<P>
 Those other pleasures will include lunch prepared by Chef Michael Hutchings 
and entertainment provided by civic members. There will also be a fashion show 
and auction. It will all take place at the Santa Barbara Polo and Racquet Club, 
3375 Foothill Road in Carpinteria, from 11 a.m.-3:30 p.m. Tickets are $125. 
Call 962-1922. 
