efficient business hotel in a nice suburban location. It earns marks for its 
proximity to outstanding restaurants and many Fortune 500 companies. Rooms: 20 
Service: 18 Dining: 17 Facilities: 17 Cost: $113 Top-Rated Hotels 
</P>
