 RITZ-CARLTON DEARBORN 300 Town Center Drive; (800) 241-3333 This luxury hotel 
is known for pampering its guests. Located next to the Fairlane Plaza Shopping 
Center and five minutes from historic Greenfield Village, this is the place 
people go when they are looking for something a cut above other area hotels. 
Rooms: 24 Service: 23 Dining: 23 Facilities: 24 Cost: $162 
</P>
