 TOWNSEND HOTEL 100 Townsend St., Birmingham; (800) 548-4172 This charming 
suites-only hotel in the suburbs has an English-countryside feel to it. 
Afternoon tea is served in the lobby. Known for excellent value and pleasant 
service. Rooms: 24 Service: 23 Dining: 21 Facilities: 22 Cost: $152 
</P>
